<div class="container section" style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 80px 20px;">
    <h1 style="font-family: var(--font-heading); text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 50px; letter-spacing: 2px;">Return & Refund Policy</h1>
    
    <div style="font-family: var(--font-body); line-height: 1.8; color: #444; font-size: 0.95rem;">
        
        <h3 style="margin-top: 30px; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 1.1rem; color: #000;">1. Custom Stitching</h3>
        <p>Due to the personalized nature of custom tailoring, <strong>we do not offer returns or refunds</strong> on stitched garments once the fabric has been cut.</p>
        <p>However, we offer <strong>free alterations</strong> if the garment does not fit according to the measurements provided at the time of booking.</p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 30px; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 1.1rem; color: #000;">2. Ready-made Products</h3>
        <p>For ready-made items (like Laces, Latkans, or Ready-to-wear standard sizes):</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Returns are accepted within <strong>3 days</strong> of delivery.</li>
            <li>The item must be unused, unwashed, and in original condition.</li>
            <li>Return shipping charges are borne by the customer unless the item is defective.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 30px; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 1.1rem; color: #000;">3. Defective Items</h3>
        <p>If you receive a damaged product or a wrong design, please contact us on WhatsApp (+91 72504 70009) within 24 hours with photos. We will arrange a replacement or repair.</p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 30px; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 1.1rem; color: #000;">4. Cancellation</h3>
        <p>Custom orders can only be cancelled within 2 hours of booking. Once cutting begins, orders cannot be cancelled.</p>

